Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.90,0:01:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站在联合军前头的抚子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.15,0:02:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也被敌军当成杀父仇人般集中攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.72,0:02:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然对方不肯罢休  我们也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.14,0:02:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彻彻底底地干掉他们！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.35,0:02:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国家的兴亡就全靠我们的奋斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.63,0:02:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.57,0:02:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提起精神提起精神
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.77,0:02:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会输给他们的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.99,0:02:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.20,0:02:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部AESTIVALIS都已出击
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.80,0:02:27.75,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,0)\bord0\shad0\1c&HF0FFFF&\pos(338,380)\fscy160\fs59\1a&H10&}那『忘不了的日子』
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.77,0:02:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始攻击!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.98,0:02:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  逮到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.45,0:02:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.27,0:02:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.28,0:02:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的混帐蜥蜴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.85,0:02:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员撤离
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.07,0:02:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部攻击都是从抚子来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.82,0:02:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.08,0:02:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岂有此理!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.48,0:03:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  发生什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.33,0:03:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AESTIVALIS连友军也攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.46,0:03:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻击友军!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.40,0:03:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻击诱导装置没有异常
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.12,0:03:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抚子的AESTIVALIS全都在攻击敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.67,0:03:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人  敌人是那边吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.97,0:03:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AESTIVALIS正在对敌军与联合军双方进行攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.49,0:03:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么  攻击停止停止
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.60,0:03:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人在极近距离
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.00,0:03:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在停止攻击的话我方会全军覆没
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.93,0:03:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  攻击敌人  只要攻击敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.45,0:03:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是打算攻击敌人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.11,0:03:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是怎么会变成这样呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.53,0:03:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  想点办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.21,0:03:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  顺其自然吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.64,0:03:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在干什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.10,0:03:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抚子本身没有受到攻击真是不幸中的大幸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.01,0:04:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之各人照顾好自己  出动支援的AESTIVALIS
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.82,0:04:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没有驾驶员了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.16,0:04:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.63,0:04:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该我出场了!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.15,0:04:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辅佐舰长  这是副官的职责
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.00,0:04:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不只是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.01,0:04:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百合香
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.92,0:04:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要保护你！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.97,0:04:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百合香！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯  请回答  纯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.17,0:04:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这天的战斗真是乱七八糟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.72,0:04:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌方也被不分敌我攻击的抚子搞迷糊了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.42,0:04:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就中止了攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.36,0:04:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想被抚子莫名其妙的攻击  联合军也撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.37,0:04:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何大家平安无事就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.45,0:05:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AESTIVALIS也几乎只有擦伤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.32,0:05:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  这个太惨了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.21,0:05:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯  为什么你要上去？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.44,0:05:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  你想说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.43,0:05:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是手语
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.20,0:05:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说在人手不足的抚子上这是身为副官的义务
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.32,0:05:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个随便你  可是驾驶时要穿战斗服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.40,0:05:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说什么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.36,0:05:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是为了百合香…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.20,0:05:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是为了百合香最好也还是穿上战斗服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.07,0:05:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今  我不想跟你罗嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.83,0:05:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  别多说了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.50,0:05:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.60,0:05:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶AESTIVALIS的时候至少要系上安全带
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.46,0:05:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好脖子伤得不严重
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.00,0:05:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过暂时无法说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.08,0:06:02.12,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是只能现在说说的台词
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.12,0:06:05.16,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要说的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.16,0:06:08.10,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一直以来对百合香的爱慕之情而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.34,0:06:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白痴!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.52,0:06:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯  加油喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.92,0:06:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要以为没人伤亡就可以高兴了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.28,0:06:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道这战舰一艘多少钱吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.51,0:06:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那个是我打下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.87,0:06:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.25,0:06:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这艘毛地黄比抚子还贵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.25,0:06:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也打下了五十架
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.53,0:06:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就光而言很不错了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.70,0:06:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.76,0:06:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.77,0:06:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔细一看每架都有联合军的标志
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.58,0:06:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.45,0:06:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.04,0:06:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说我的击落数吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.94,0:06:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一共78架
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.21,0:06:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌我两方加起来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.06,0:06:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,62架是我方的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.14,0:06:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.33,0:06:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人你从刚才就一直没说话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.02,0:06:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那..那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.68,0:06:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没大家那么惨啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.29,0:06:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本来打算攻击敌军的郁金香
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.82,0:07:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是被摧毁的却是联合军燃料基地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.27,0:07:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道那基地的建筑费吗!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.45,0:07:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些不是都有保险吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.11,0:07:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.29,0:07:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是至少要花慰问金吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.85,0:07:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过无论如何我方无人伤亡真是奇迹般的幸运
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.39,0:07:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慰问金要再增加的话真不知要怎么办了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.62,0:07:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过有一名脑震荡后遗症的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.33,0:07:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那主要的原因是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.54,0:07:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会攻击联合军呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.07,0:07:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们又不是故意去做的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.95,0:07:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们所爱的是绿色的地球
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.32,0:07:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们决不可能背叛联合军的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.97,0:07:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说是整备不良?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.14,0:07:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这话我可不能当做没听见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.74,0:07:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说我们的安全整备有漏洞是不是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.77,0:07:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经过连日的战斗多少都会有些失误吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.35,0:07:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维修部门的疲劳度也不容忽视啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.94,0:07:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管疲劳不疲劳  整备的失误是会出人命的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.84,0:07:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整备的好坏可是事关人命！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.90,0:08:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我虽然在女人方面是失败  但机械的整备我决不会失败
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别把你们的失误都怪到我们头上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.48,0:08:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.30,0:08:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶员或整备士都没有出错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.85,0:08:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那原因是什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.78,0:08:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  调查此事的联合军调查团正朝我们这边来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.35,0:08:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们一直唠叨是不是抚子的防卫攻击电脑出了问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.94,0:08:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.87,0:08:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.79,0:08:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道  我什么都没做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.42,0:08:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从调查船逃出的救生艇正在求救
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.55,0:08:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  又有攻击命令了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.09,0:08:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁下的命令?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.65,0:08:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.69,0:08:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以打  那个不是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.08,0:09:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收容地球军调查船救生艇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.15,0:09:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被抚子误射的调查员们也不可能冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.42,0:09:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,片面斥责抚子的缺陷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.91,0:09:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之说别人坏话是最轻松的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.34,0:09:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用多说  电脑有学习机能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.33,0:09:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会根据经历进行学习并采取最妥善的行动措施
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.90,0:09:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抚子的电脑是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.60,0:09:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是"思兼"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.96,0:09:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是电脑的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.37,0:09:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给只不过是道具的电脑取名字
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.40,0:09:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是二十世纪末的恶习
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.44,0:09:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是思兼就是思兼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.93,0:09:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是重钟（音同思兼）还是轻钟都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.52,0:09:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之抚子的电脑中有过去突破防卫线的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.84,0:09:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说它已经把联合军是妨碍抚子行动的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.62,0:09:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这段记忆学起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.30,0:10:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此与地球联合军共同作战时会产生抗拒反应
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.94,0:10:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿人类来打比方的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.21,0:10:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像无论日夜假期不停充电上班
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.30,0:10:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而导致过度疲劳的白领一族一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.80,0:10:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个比喻真是简单易懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.35,0:10:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了  我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.98,0:10:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作压力积累过多的话人就会崩溃的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.88,0:10:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电脑的话则会进入冻结状态
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.65,0:10:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是只是冻结的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.14,0:10:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要把变成BUG的资料消掉再重新设定就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.37,0:10:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思兼具有自动重新设定功能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.51,0:10:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这电脑所学习的对联合军的敌对意识太深了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.45,0:10:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次重新设定就会增加压力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.74,0:10:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是演变成了这次的攻击行动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.34,0:10:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解决的方法只有完全消除学习到的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.91,0:10:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后改写新的程式
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.38,0:10:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.88,0:10:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.33,0:10:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样随随便便可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.28,0:10:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样做的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.63,0:10:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抚子好不容易到火星所学到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.53,0:11:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合理有效地应对与敌人的战斗的记忆也会被消除
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.88,0:11:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抚子是隶属联合军的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.80,0:11:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单独行动时的记忆是百害而无一利
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.60,0:11:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.08,0:11:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且为了保卫地球而战的是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.46,0:11:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是机器
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.85,0:11:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用说  抚子是在联合军旗下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.63,0:11:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须让它忘掉与联合军敌对的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.70,0:11:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘掉就是彻底舍去…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.96,0:11:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是大人的借口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.02,0:11:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对自己不利的事情只要忘掉就好的借口
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.00,0:11:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人们都好狡猾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.48,0:11:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉璃…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.36,0:11:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什.什..什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.22,0:11:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么所有人都一副打扮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.86,0:11:56.95,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord0}抚子电脑控制室
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.02,0:11:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切换成由副电脑管制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.35,0:11:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安装开始
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.98,0:12:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不消除所有的资料就不行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.41,0:12:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.66,0:12:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.94,0:12:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改写让思兼绝对服从的程式
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.08,0:12:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抚子从此就脱胎换骨了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.68,0:12:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊  从民用船变成真正的战舰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.39,0:12:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只为军方工作的船
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.58,0:12:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明..人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.72,0:12:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啊   你这家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.10,0:12:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事情要拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.50,0:12:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能麻烦你跟我来一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.81,0:12:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.99,0:12:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.09,0:12:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没有放弃当厨师呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.99,0:12:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战以外的时间我要练习做料理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.00,0:12:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我需要AESTIVALIS的驾驶员啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.58,0:12:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找谁都好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.02,0:12:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像凉子啦  光  泉  赤…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.88,0:12:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.03,0:12:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非得是天河不可
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.59,0:12:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.13,0:12:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.31,0:12:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好臭喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.74,0:12:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.37,0:12:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生都是这样子吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.66,0:12:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这房间真讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.89,0:12:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.10,0:13:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,控制室都被占据了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.99,0:13:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样危险的事又不能在舰桥做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.55,0:13:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那里小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.57,0:13:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我辛苦做的模型
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.50,0:13:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里可以做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.02,0:13:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个消除BUG什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.25,0:13:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然外表不怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.74,0:13:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我已经跟思兼连线过不知几次了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.59,0:13:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,程式做得很好  看着也不会腻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.65,0:13:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.56,0:13:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.68,0:13:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AESTIVALIS?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.29,0:13:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的印象程式
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.33,0:13:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是能进入思兼的程式之内
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.36,0:13:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调查和修复有问题的地方的所谓电脑空间的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.90,0:13:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必杀扫除人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.75,0:13:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.70,0:13:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么  对我的兴趣有意见吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.62,0:13:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要跟我的主电脑连线  然后操控模拟器
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.30,0:13:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就变成优秀的电脑战士了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.24,0:13:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我来支援
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.40,0:13:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.88,0:13:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.79,0:13:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河AESTI启动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.42,0:13:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.59,0:14:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是电脑里面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.62,0:14:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是被我影像化的电脑记忆中枢镜象
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.76,0:14:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回想起来这是参照我失败七次的麻省理工学院图书馆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.94,0:14:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该往哪里走呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.53,0:14:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来带路
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.13,0:14:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.59,0:14:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边上去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.10,0:14:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右转
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.64,0:14:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.96,0:14:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的地是思兼的自主意识部分
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.33,0:14:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是正在覆盖中的新的军方程式
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.86,0:14:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那干掉它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.57,0:14:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.96,0:14:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在攻击新程式的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.42,0:14:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安装会停止
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.96,0:14:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抚子会和原来一样继续反抗地球军
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.44,0:14:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.03,0:14:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先往前头
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.44,0:14:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去思兼的自主意识部分
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.12,0:14:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.90,0:14:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点不太忍心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.79,0:14:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很善良呢  天河
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.57,0:14:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.22,0:15:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.35,0:15:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思兼的自主意识部分
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.55,0:15:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的抚子身为抚子的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.73,0:15:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己确定自己存在的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.19,0:15:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己存在的证明?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.45,0:15:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己最重要的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.87,0:15:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想忘也忘不了的最重要的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.93,0:15:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记忆… 回忆…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.09,0:15:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想忘记也忘不了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.07,0:15:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己确定自己存在的证明吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.20,0:15:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让它稍微忘掉一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.22,0:15:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让它忘记?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.06,0:15:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.83,0:15:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个伸出来的部份
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.19,0:15:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请把那部份剪掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.35,0:15:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然悲哀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.82,0:15:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过枝芽还会再长出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.48,0:15:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一天思兼会记起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.36,0:15:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后抚子不会改变自己的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.81,0:15:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.05,0:15:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思兼  稍微忘记些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.38,0:15:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后长大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.88,0:16:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只要假装服从联合军
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.72,0:16:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抚子仍然还是抚子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.20,0:16:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.23,0:16:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.15,0:16:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  明人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.40,0:16:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于出来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.31,0:16:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么出来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.75,0:16:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电脑的异物排除意识
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.20,0:16:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是思兼的自卫反应
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.06,0:16:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是不想忘记重要记忆的能量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.90,0:16:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.35,0:16:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.21,0:16:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激钢人3
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.87,0:16:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.18,0:16:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是在思兼输入的资料中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.11,0:16:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最强  最正确的  正义的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.37,0:16:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思兼把他当成是自己的伙伴了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.16,0:16:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为思兼和你一起看过激钢人的录影带
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.34,0:16:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这样也用着变成激钢人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.62,0:17:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为最了解激钢人的人是你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.54,0:17:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要我跟激钢人战斗吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.19,0:17:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜抚了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.67,0:17:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊  明人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.77,0:17:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把激钢人什么的干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.58,0:17:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.59,0:17:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你  请战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.91,0:17:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.43,0:17:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方似乎不想放过你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.87,0:17:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激钢光束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.98,0:17:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激钢飞切
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.73,0:17:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  打不过他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.42,0:17:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方是激钢人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.36,0:17:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会赢的  天河一定可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.70,0:17:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对那个机器人的思念应该比思兼更强
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.47,0:17:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的..思念
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.73,0:17:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.53,0:17:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激钢人!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.29,0:17:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威力不相上下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.98,0:17:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激钢光束
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.39,0:18:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激钢飞踢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.50,0:18:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样分不出胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.22,0:18:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  由人来操纵的我方比较不利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.10,0:18:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.26,0:18:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为人类的天河对那机器人从很久以前就非常了解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.63,0:18:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且一直喜爱着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.34,0:18:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明人的思念是不可能输的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.61,0:18:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的话真让我高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.74,0:18:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从很久以前  一直喜爱着…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.18,0:18:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.40,0:18:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.52,0:18:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激钢人从第十七集开始换成激钢人V…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.27,0:18:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.64,0:18:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦幻的变形模式!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.52,0:18:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙钢人你知道吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.33,0:19:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之焰！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.67,0:19:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自卫反应消灭  记忆修正完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.04,0:19:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河  还有就是尽快去解决新程式
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.96,0:19:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去一切都会被消除的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.23,0:19:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.40,0:19:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是这样做没问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.32,0:19:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被那些家伙发现的话就麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.49,0:19:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.24,0:19:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚刚就对调查团的电脑输入假资料了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.30,0:19:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管放手干吧  明人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.45,0:19:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.25,0:19:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙钢人只有设定资料
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.33,0:19:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并没有在电视上出现过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.35,0:19:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也只是在凯的设定专辑里看过而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.19,0:19:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.08,0:19:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天河的信念真的很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.10,0:20:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是很有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.66,0:20:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.60,0:20:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后  抚子的电脑思兼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.71,0:20:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然还有抚子自身都没有发现任何异状
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.21,0:20:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺利顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.82,0:20:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场战争地球会赢的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.54,0:20:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧  舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.04,0:20:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那当然
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.64,0:20:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.41,0:20:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.65,0:20:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微速前进  右满舵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.11,0:20:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微速前进  右满舵
