Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.81,0:20:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.65,0:21:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充满速度感心跳加速的冒险
